refactor: migrate from LangChain4j to MCP SDK for LLM operations

- Replace LangChain4j dependencies with MCP Kotlin SDK (0.5.0)
- Add McpLlmClient for stdio-based MCP server communication
- Refactor GameService and PuzzleService to use McpLlmClient
- Remove LangChain4j AI Service interfaces (GameMasterService, SolutionValidator, etc)
- Update Settings to use McpConfig instead of GeminiConfig/PuzzleGeneratorConfig
- Security layer now delegated to mcp-llm-server (common for 20q + turtle-soup)
